title: Astralasia - Special World
description:
Official video of the Astralasia single 'Special World'. Full version of the track is on the Astralasia album 'White Bird'.
Released in 1998 on Magick Eye Records and available to download or stream from legal digital sites. Also available on CD & vinyl from http://www.magickeye.com

For further info on astralasia and magickeyemusic please visit and like facebook pages.
